e-link interwiki-tr mw-list-item"><a href="https://tr.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C4%B0svi%C3%A7re_Film_%C3%96d%C3%BCl%C3%BC" title="İsviçre Film Ödülü – Turkish" lang="tr" hreflang="tr" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>Türkçe</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-uk mw-list-item"><a href="https://uk.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A8%D0%B2%D0%B5%D0%B9%D1%86%D0%B0%D1%80%D1%81%D1%8C%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D0%BA%D1%96%D0%BD%D0%BE%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%BC%D1%96%D1%8F" title="Швейцарська кінопремія – Ukrainian" lang="uk" hreflang="uk" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>Українська</span></a></li>
